<h1>LocalLibrary <% title %> </h1>
<p>Welcome to LocalLibrary, a very basic Express website developed as a tutorial example on the Mozilla Developer Network.</p>

<h1>Dynamic content</h1>

<% if(error) { %> 
<p>Error getting dynamic content!</p> 
<%} else { %>
    <p>The libraryhas the following record counts:</p>

    <ul>
        <li><span class="bld">Books: </span>  <%= data.book_count %> </li>
        <li><span class="bld">Copies: </span>  <%= data.book_instance_count %> </li>
        <li><span class="bld">Copies Avaliable: </span> <%= data.book_instance_available_count %> </li>
        <li><span class="bld">Authors: </span>  <%= data.author_count %> </li>
        <li><span class="bld">Genres: </span>  <%= data.genre_count %> </li>
    </ul>

<% } %>  